-- Yahoo names Balogh as technology chief
-- 
-- Tue Jan 29, 2008 5:05pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/29/us-yahoo-cto-idUSWNAS833720080129

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Yahoo Inc ( YHOO.O ) on Tuesday named Aristotle Balogh as its new chief technology officer, a position from which he will manage the company's technology operations and product development. 

 Balogh, 43, will be based at Yahoo headquarters in Sunnyvale, Calif., and report directly to Chief Executive Jerry Yang, the company said. Balogh was previously the CTO of VeriSign Inc ( VRSN.O ). (Reporting by  Paul Thomasch )